{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 18,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they did theirs on 3 and 4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I think they burned number 4 crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were about the only thing we knew that in the morning, you know, they tried to-- to get out, and-- and maybe get rid of the camp and go.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they couldn't do it, because the SS were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they killed 600 of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the morning we had to put them in the oven ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's the only thing I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the people-- to the people that did the revolution and the other ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I felt that we wanted to be part of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to-- and we couldn't do it, because the-- the Germans-- when-- you know, the Polish guys in number 2, they didn't want to have no part of it, because we weren't there in the beginning, so what for?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that what happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they-- they pay with their lives, 600 of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is-- is a few of them that-- they don't exist now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other was Cohen, you know, the guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These two, they wrote plenty of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a-- there is a big one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody sent me-- before he died, Mario [INAUDIBLE] sent me a note of the son of-- what's his first name-- from Cohen?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Wrote-- I have it in Greek, but I wrote about the sonderkommando, about the revolution.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- you can-- I can give it to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can [INAUDIBLE] and do it-- you can do the translation from Greek to English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the-- about the revolution?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You mean, when I was there?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
